          Read the full AGPL-3.0 license text <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card card-primary">
    <div class="card-header">
      <i class="fas fa-code"></i> Tech Stack
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p>{{ siteName }} is built with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> PHP 8.1+, Symfony 4.2</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> MySQL, Redis, Elasticsearch</li>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Bootstrap 4, Webpack, ES6</li>
        <li><strong>Discord:</strong> Discord API v10, DiscordPHP</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card card-primary">
    <div class="card-header">
      <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i> Contributing
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p>
        Contributions are welcome! Whether it's bug reports, feature requests, or code contributions,
